        public static void setPrintModel(boolean id,
                                 boolean fName,
                                 boolean lName,
                                 boolean grade,
                                 boolean hours,
                                 boolean csaCat)
                          throws java.lang.Exception
        Sets the print table model with selected columns and rows.
        Parameters:
        id - If the ID column should be included in the print table model
        fName - If the first name column should be included in the print table model
        lName - If the last name column should be included in the print table model
        grade - If the grade column should be included in the print table model
        hours - If the hours column should be included in the print table model
        csaCat - If the CSA column should be included in the print table model
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - If no column or row is selected

      • selectAll

        public static void selectAll(boolean toSelect)
        Selects or deselects all rows of the report table.
        Parameters:
        toSelect - If true, all rows will be selected. If false, all rows will be deselected

      • selection

        public static void selection(java.lang.String selectionType,
                             boolean freshman,
                             boolean sophomore,
                             boolean junior,
                             boolean senior,
                             boolean none,
                             boolean service,
                             boolean community,
                             boolean achievement)
        Filters data based on what categories are selected. If "One" is selected, at least one category needs to be selected. If "Both" is selected, only one grade and one CSA category can be selected.
        Parameters:
        selectionType - "One" or "Both"
        freshman - If the grade freshman is selected for filtering
        sophomore - If the grade sophomore is selected for filtering
        junior - If the grade junior is selected for filtering
        senior - If the grade senior is selected for filtering
        none - If the CSA category none is selected for filtering
        service - If the CSA category service is selected for filtering
        community - If the CSA category community is selected for filtering
        achievement - If the CSA category achievement is selected for filtering
